到真相：</h2>受害者可能成为罪犯，而嫌疑人只是犯罪链中的一个环节。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感受错误决定的后果：</h2>你准备好为拯救挚爱之人而亲自犯罪了吗？<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435670/extras/b0e94a320c6d942a960c078f7d6ab432.poster.avif?t=1769408189\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435670/extras/b0e94a320c6d942a960c078f7d6ab432.webm?t=1769408189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435670/extras/b0e94a320c6d942a960c078f7d6ab432.mp4?t=1769408189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435670/extras/0874d8d207086933a3f6e726d9509076.webp?t=1769408189\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435670/extras/0874d8d207086933a3f6e726d9509076.poster.avif?t=1769408189\" class=\"bb_img\" width=420 height=26 /></picture></span>",
